      • convertLinks2Records

        void convertLinks2Records()
        Browse all the set to convert all the items into records. It converts only items that already loaded into memory from storage. To convert records that will be fetched from disk later use OAutoConvertToRecord.setAutoConvertToRecord(boolean)
